generatedFromSchema_doNotEdit.title: World Filter Group Map
generatedFromSchema_doNotEdit.description: Filters allow data objects to specify test criteria which allows their use. Filters can be defined by a single object of type (Filter Test), an array of tests, collection groups, or a combination of these objects.

fields.description: Evaluates all tests in the group, all must pass in order for the group to pass.
